name: sectionBuilder
description: function to create a section design
parameters: {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'title': {'type': 'string', 'description': 'the title of the section if any'}, 'titleBool': {'type': 'string', 'description': 'if this section should have a title', 'enum': ['TRUE', 'FALSE']}, 'bgColor': {'type': 'string', 'description': 'the background color of the section in RGB list format. eg. white = [255,255,255]'}, 'sectionPreset': {'type': 'string', 'description': 'the widget type this section should use', 'enum': ['Carousel', 'HorizontalList', 'VerticalList', 'Grid']}}}
